Class MESpeciesReference

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sbml.jsbml.AbstractTreeNode

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, javax.swing.tree.TreeNode, org.sbml.jsbml.util.TreeNodeWithChangeSupport, MEConstants

    public class MESpeciesReference
extends MEAbstractXMLNodePlugin
implements MEConstants
    Implements methods and attributes to create and add lists of reactants and products to SubreactionData objects and StoichiometricData objects for the MEProcessData.
    Author:
    Marc A. Voigt

      • createMESpeciesReference

        public org.sbml.jsbml.xml.XMLNode createMESpeciesReference(java.lang.String speciesReference,
                                                           double stoichiometry)
        Create an XMLNode of the new MESpeciesReference for the given species and stoichiometry.

        These are used for the lists of products and reactants in the MEProcessData.

        Parameters:
        speciesReference - the id of the new speciesReference
        stoichiometry - the stoichiometry of the species in the process
        Returns:
        the XMLNode of the MESpeciesReference
